<body>
  <h1>Inspiro</h1>
  <p>Inspiro helps you turn ideas into visuals. Enter a prompt, discover inspiring images, and automatically save curated selections to your Pinterest boards.</p>

  <h2>What it does</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Searches Pinterest (with Unsplash fallback)</li>
    <li>Ranks & de-duplicates images</li>
    <li>Creates Pins on your chosen board</li>
    <li>Optional logging to Google Sheets</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Privacy</h2>
  <p>Read our policy: <a href="https://ashhh0120.github.io/inspiro-privacy-policy/">inspiro-privacy-policy</a></p>

